<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Summerhill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Green spaces and natural parks are what drives people to properties in this neighborhood of Airdrie. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Summerhill homes for sale have a starting price in the range of early 300s to mid 400s. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Buying a home in Summerhill is therefore relatively cheaper than the rest of the region. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The green spaces and parks in Summerhill neighborhood provide a great place to play with kids, walk pets, and spend time being close to nature. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Large bungalows, condos, and detached homes form a part of Summerhill real estate listings. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">It's certainly one of the most comfortable neighborhoods to live in Airdrie.</p>
        </div>
